{
  "info": {
    "name": "Multi RAG-Platform",
    "description": "API collection for the Multi RAG-Platform — a chatbot builder with RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) using Google Gemini + LangChain + pgvector.\n\n## Setup\n1. Register a user via `POST /api/auth/register`\n2. Login via `POST /api/auth/login` and copy the token\n3. Set the `token` variable in the collection (or use the login response's auto-set script)\n4. Create a bot via `POST /api/bots/create`\n5. Add knowledge sources via text, file upload, or URL\n6. Chat with your bot via `POST /api/chat/:botId`\n7. Embed the widget via `GET /widget/:embedKey/config`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:4000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "botId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "knowledgeSourceId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "conversationId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "embedKey",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "messageId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "resetToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
